250
00:25:30,054 --> 00:25:32,114
Hello, Polo.

251
00:25:32,523 --> 00:25:33,752
Hello.

252
00:25:41,232 --> 00:25:42,996
It's very nice.

253
00:25:49,106 --> 00:25:52,201
