291
00:28:55,659 --> 00:28:57,127
<i>Hello?</i>

292
00:28:57,495 --> 00:29:00,124
<i>Hello? Hello?</i>

293
00:29:00,765 --> 00:29:02,233
<i>Hello?</i>

294
00:29:03,801 --> 00:29:05,997
- Hi.
- Hi.

